                <note rend="inline" type="source">852.00/2780: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bowers</hi>
                    </persName>), <hi rend="italic">Then in France</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-08-25T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 25, 1936—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>B–6. Your August 24, 11 a.m., and your 76, August 25, noon. I approve your
                    decision not to attend this meeting. As regards the question of your attendance
                    at any future meetings, I feel that I must leave the matter to your discretion.
                    You may, of course, consult me about any particular meeting.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
